scenes.description: Mori Calliope discusses the purchase benefits for her upcoming Blu-ray release, 'NEW ORDER', pointing at a large informative board.
A full-screen view of the 'NEW ORDER' release information and shop-specific benefits.
Calliope notices a phone prop in the 3D room starting to ring.
Calliope answers the phone and talks to IRyS, who is calling in.
IRyS 'arrives' in the room as a flat 2D avatar. They joke about her appearance and choose a song to sing.
